	* FormattingStrategy/CSharpIndentEngine.cs: A few fixes, including
	one for bug #82055.

	* Gui/CSharpTextEditorExtension.cs (IsInUsing): Simplified.
	(GetPreviousToken): Fixed bug #82131.

