	* Parser/TypeVisitor.cs, Parser/SharpDevelopTree/ReturnType.cs: Take
	  into account that the parser returns array dimensions starting at
	  0, not at 1.  Fixed some issues when resolving indexer types. Fixes
	  bug #79382.
